# B 11/11
~~我生日哎。~~

数位最多两位，这个数位分解很简单。这里有一种简单粗暴的办法：如果十位是0就让它等于个位就好了，反正不影响结果。

{% spoiler ACCode %}

```cpp
#include <bits/stdc++.h>

using namespace std;

const int N = 110;
int n, d[N], ans;

int main() {
	scanf("%d", &n);
	for (int i = 1;i <= n;i++) {
		scanf("%d", &d[i]);
		for (int j = 1;j <= d[i];j++) {
			int ge = j % 10, shi = j / 10, gei = i % 10, shii = i /10;
			if (shi == 0)
				shi = ge;
			if (shii == 0)
				shii = gei;
			if (ge == shi && shi == gei && gei == shii)
				ans++;
		}
	}
	printf("%d\n", ans);
	return 0;
}
